278
00:21:56.369 --> 00:21:57.680
On board ship. we kept cuts.

279
00:22:02.220 --> 00:22:03.160
Steal yourself.

280
00:22:04.679 --> 00:22:08.180
You must guard our intent. whilst I
quietly...

281
00:22:09.669 --> 00:22:11.140
investigate hiring a ship.

282
00:22:12.179 --> 00:22:13.280
