289
00:23:05.700 --> 00:23:08.240
As many have gathered. we are the
dispossessed of the war.

290
00:23:09.120 --> 00:23:09.940
You river folk!

291
00:23:12.814 --> 00:23:15.480
I fucking hate river folk.

292
00:23:16.879 --> 00:23:18.040
We hail from Sharpe Point.

293
00:23:18.040 --> 00:23:18.080
We are the dispossessed of the land.

294
00:23:19.259 --> 00:23:20.840
Prince Eamon burned it to the ground.

295
00:23:22.400 --> 00:23:23.380
With his...

296
00:23:27.899 --> 00:23:28.640
How did you get out?

297
00:23:29.360 --> 00:23:30.300
We nearly didn't.

298
00:23:33.190 --> 00:23:34.040
As you can see.

299
00:23:47.760 --> 00:23:48.380
Well...

300
00:23:49.130 --> 00:23:49.860
We're too many.

301
00:23:51.020 --> 00:23:51.840
Fuck off.

302
