309
00:24:18.180 --> 00:24:18.720
A little.

310
00:24:23.319 --> 00:24:24.060
Maybe you'll be useful.

311
00:24:25.454 --> 00:24:26.760
I have the command around here.

312
00:24:27.609 --> 00:24:28.600
Oh. then much is clear.

313
00:24:29.460 --> 00:24:30.240
My lord.

314
00:24:31.049 --> 00:24:32.600
Tangle Tongue works the latrines.

315
00:24:33.729 --> 00:24:34.820
Collects piss for the tanners.

316
00:24:35.080 --> 00:24:36.160
Shit for the farmers.

317
00:24:37.979 --> 00:24:38.780
This one can help him.

318
00:24:40.020 --> 00:24:40.980
Separate buckets.

319
00:24:41.440 --> 00:24:42.180
Mix it up.

320
00:24:42.340 --> 00:24:43.060
They won't pay.

321
00:24:44.460 --> 00:24:44.980
I...

322
00:24:46.019 --> 00:24:47.600
Won't touch the fucking latrines.

323
00:24:48.000 --> 00:24:49.340
Just do as I say. Gregor.

324
00:24:49.460 --> 00:24:51.120
I can read just as well as he can.

325
00:24:51.239 --> 00:24:52.900
Tangle Tongue and Mangle Face!

326
00:24:57.860 --> 00:24:58.720
You'll be good together.

327
00:24:59.059 --> 00:25:01.560
It's not bad once you're used to it.
brother.

328
00:25:07.280 --> 00:25:07.920
Come on.

329
00:25:09.020 --> 00:25:09.900
Fuck off!

330
00:25:20.349 --> 00:25:21.980
I think we'll have a nice time here.
lads.

331
00:25:22.249 --> 00:25:23.120
You'll make Barry tonight.

332
00:25:23.719 --> 00:25:24.440
You'll be better than Honey Hope.

333
00:25:36.380 --> 00:25:36.820
Wait.

334
00:25:45.869 --> 00:25:47.040
I need to inspect the goods.

335
00:25:56.759 --> 00:25:57.840
Go if I just summarize me.

336
00:26:12.800 --> 00:26:15.120
Take your hands off of her!

337
00:26:16.280 --> 00:26:17.280
Get off of her!

338
00:26:25.390 --> 00:26:25.870
Get her out!

339
00:26:26.190 --> 00:26:27.570
Get her out!

340
00:26:38.439 --> 00:26:39.420
Sir Hugh Hammer. your grace.

341
00:26:41.719 --> 00:26:45.820
Sir Hugh. I assure you. when there is news
