Take it in turn between you.

350
00:27:12.329 --> 00:27:14.210
Keep watch on the town and on each other.

351
00:27:14.749 --> 00:27:15.750
You may take the first post.

352
00:27:16.449 --> 00:27:17.750
See that Ulf is alerted to the plan.

353
00:27:19.830 --> 00:27:20.510
Your grace.

354
00:27:35.549 --> 00:27:36.170
What's it say?

355
00:27:40.439 --> 00:27:41.400
Queen of bastards.

356
00:27:43.319 --> 00:27:46.260
Hightower loyalists. trying to fight a war
