357
00:27:54.039 --> 00:27:55.540
He has returned!

358
00:28:06.850 --> 00:28:08.050
More god than man.

359
00:28:08.599 --> 00:28:11.570
Hey. will you honor your friends with a
round of drinks. my lord?

360
